channel.title: Interesting FM or FoL that are worth to look in
channel.description:
My request is in title.
I would like to look into cases that were including very well at least one of the factors like: Scumreads/Deduction or Teamwork regardless of the alignment.
If you have any good examples on this is site please let me know and which factor is included(Can be multiplied). :male_detective:
And I’m talking about past games.
